Hi Daniel,

Last week I asked our community, Whats a win youve had recently?

Eriks response shows licensing in motion:

"To pick one win is difficult...

Everything inventRight shares with and teaches the inventing community is a massive WIN for all of us. What I find as my biggest win, is having the knowledge to pitch any concept I develop to as many companies as I can find. 

Most recently I've used this knowledge (power) to gain interest in 4 of my concepts from 8 different companies.

Thank you so much Stephen, Andrew, and the entire inventRight crew!"

Erik S., inventRight Member

Heres the part I hope you dont miss: Capability creates conversations.

Erik applied what he's learned as an inventRight Member, clearly and consistently, and 8 companies leaned in.

To everyone reading, choose one next step and take it today.

Momentum comes from progress.
